column3: Golf-course Road (0.45KM) Asphalt concrete, kerbing, drainage and walkways were already completed. Street light works was on-going. Road marking and road signs works were yet to be executed. The entire walkways and drainage were untidy.

Peter Paul Opok Road (0.897km) Asphalt concrete and drainage were completed from Km 0+070 to the end; walkways were being finalised. Street lights works was on-going. Road marking and road signs works were yet to be executed. The entire walkways and drainage were untidy.
